Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.69,0:03:40.57,Jigoku_OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\an3\fad(150,150)}堂々巡りの最中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.57,0:03:42.74,Jigoku_OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}労働鼠の性だ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.74,0:03:43.99,Jigoku_OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Wake Up Bankers
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.99,0:03:44.53,Jigoku_OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Pay Back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.53,0:03:45.70,Jigoku_OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}今日も労働
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.70,0:03:47.16,Jigoku_OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}One verse One punch
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.33,0:03:49.41,Jigoku_OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}AnswerにはFantasyを
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.54,0:03:51.41,Jigoku_OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Stand up my fav people
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.21,0:03:56.75,Jigoku_OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(150,150)}許してくれ　嘗て犯した科を
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.75,0:04:01.34,Jigoku_OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}裁いてくれ　真新しい良し悪しで
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.34,0:04:05.68,Jigoku_OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}諭してくれ　どうせ助かったのなら
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.68,0:04:11.39,Jigoku_OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}愛する人を介してこの世の絶景が拝みたい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.02,0:04:15.98,Jigoku_OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}さあ今日は今日で明日は又明日
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.61,0:04:20.78,Jigoku_OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(150,150)}煩って行こうぞ　生身の流離
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.15,0:04:25.37,Jigoku_OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}色即是空です　瞬く間に移ろう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.78,0:04:30.12,Jigoku_OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}万歳鼓動が　ほら玉響果敢ない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.37,0:03:06.45,Jigoku_OPTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\an7\fscx120\fscy80\fax-0.08}變換自如的生命  將一切釋放
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.79,0:03:10.96,Jigoku_OPTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\fscx120\fscy80\fax-0.08}沒有實體  殘缺未完
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:15.46,Jigoku_OPTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\fscx120\fscy80\fax-0.08}名字直指本質  流言一併吞沒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.00,0:03:20.26,Jigoku_OPTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\fscx120\fscy80\fax-0.08}實現心願之後  前方是何模樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.26,0:03:24.76,Jigoku_OPTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\fscx120\fscy80\fax-0.08}空洞無物身體  用之即棄  直接預祝
