Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.70,0:03:47.16,Jigoku_OPTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\fscx120\fscy80\fax-0.08}一節一擊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.33,0:03:49.41,Jigoku_OPTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\fscx120\fscy80\fax-0.08}幻想即為回答
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.54,0:03:51.41,Jigoku_OPTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\fscx120\fscy80\fax-0.08}站起來吧  同胞們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.21,0:03:56.75,Jigoku_OPTC,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(150,150)\fscx120\fscy80\fax-0.08}原諒我吧  過去的罪行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.75,0:04:01.34,Jigoku_OPTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\fscx120\fscy80\fax-0.08}重新裁決  以全新的善惡觀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.34,0:04:05.68,Jigoku_OPTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\fscx120\fscy80\fax-0.08}醒悟吧  既然已經得救
