Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.15,0:04:25.37,Jigoku_OPTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\fscx120\fscy80\fax-0.08}色即是空  瞬間轉移
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.78,0:04:30.12,Jigoku_OPTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\fscx120\fscy80\fax-0.08}喝彩搏動  玉響縹緲
